					<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-4" data-i18n="integration.subtitle">
						Universal integration
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-i18n="integration.description">
						ReportButton works with any CMS or website platform. Just paste one script and you are done.
					</p>
